---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Pork Chops with Cheesy Garlic Bread and Arugula Salad
description: Juicy pork chops are drizzled with a zesty balsamic glaze that's so good, you'll want to dip your cheesy garlic bread into it, too! An arugula salad with sweet peppers brings a fresh crunch to round out the plate.
